INTRO HEADLINE: Setting new benchmarks in fan engagement and event execution
INTRO BODY:
  As the appointed project management agency for WTT Singapore Smash 2025,
  KIN took on the challenge of delivering one of Asia's premier table tennis
  events. Our mission extended beyond traditional event management — we were
  tasked with creating an unparalleled sporting experience that would set new
  benchmarks in fan engagement and event execution.

  WTT's objectives were clear: deliver state-of-the-art audio-visual
  experiences, build the best fan experience in sports events, and create an
  environment that serves both fans and players seamlessly. Starting in August
  2024, our team developed a comprehensive strategy across infrastructure,
  operations, and sustainability.

